<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:06:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联合国报告对西岸权利“迅速恶化”表示遗憾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/un-report-deplores-rapid-deterioration-of-rights-in-west-bank/0000018c-b07c-db94-afbd-b07d3aa50000</link><description>报道称，自10月7日哈马斯袭击以来，约300名巴勒斯坦人在与以色列军队或极端主义定居者的冲突中丧生。联合国专员呼吁以色列确保“有效保护巴勒斯坦社区”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 13:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/un-report-deplores-rapid-deterioration-of-rights-in-west-bank/0000018c-b07c-db94-afbd-b07d3aa50000</guid></item><item><title>尼尔奥兹幸存者离开埃拉特酒店，可能不会再回家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-survivors-leave-eilat-hotel-face-likelihood-they-wont-be-going-home-again/0000018c-af93-d45c-a98e-afdfcd590000</link><description>“当我们的生活被打破的那一天”和“国家抛弃了我们，好人就在它的位置上” ■ 在酒店找到避难所后，幸存者形成了一种奇怪的新常态，日子过得没有时间表或例行公事—— “长湿婆”为他们失去的一切</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:53:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-survivors-leave-eilat-hotel-face-likelihood-they-wont-be-going-home-again/0000018c-af93-d45c-a98e-afdfcd590000</guid></item><item><title>Nova狂欢受害者的家属拒绝再保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-families-of-the-victims-at-the-reim-party-refuse-to-keep-silent-any-longed/0000018c-acff-d22c-a98c-fcff58b50000</link><description>大屠杀发生后的几个星期里，被害者的父母保持沉默，因悲痛而瘫痪。现在，140 个家庭聚集在一起，要求以色列领导人给出答案。 “没有人有精力去战斗，但我们别无选择。我们被遗弃了，”一位家长说</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-families-of-the-victims-at-the-reim-party-refuse-to-keep-silent-any-longed/0000018c-acff-d22c-a98c-fcff58b50000</guid></item><item><title>泄露的法院判决：内塔尼亚胡的司法政变卷土重来，他的攻击再次爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/leaked-court-decision-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-and-his-attacks-are-unleashed/0000018c-b00a-d45c-a98e-bb4e27290000</link><description>就像美国最高法院关于堕胎裁决的泄密一样，以色列法官对内塔尼亚胡关键司法政变法案的泄密立场值得调查</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/leaked-court-decision-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-and-his-attacks-are-unleashed/0000018c-b00a-d45c-a98e-bb4e27290000</guid></item><item><title>星巴克如何卷入以色列-哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/how-starbucks-got-embroiled-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-b043-db94-afbd-b07b8ef20000</link><description>欢迎来到 BDS 2.0：如果你不能抵制一家以色列公司，那就以最站不住脚的理由寻找其他东西来抵制</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:04:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/how-starbucks-got-embroiled-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-b043-db94-afbd-b07b8ef20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列宣布约旦河西岸货币兑换恐怖组织扣押哈马斯数百万资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-declares-west-bank-money-exchange-terror-org-seizes-millions-of-hamas-funds/0000018c-aff3-db94-afbd-affb65040000</link><description>以色列军队突袭了约旦河西岸的9个货币兑换分行，逮捕了21名涉嫌向哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织转移资金的巴勒斯坦人。巴勒斯坦人报告说，袭击期间发生冲突，造成一人死亡、多人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 11:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-declares-west-bank-money-exchange-terror-org-seizes-millions-of-hamas-funds/0000018c-aff3-db94-afbd-affb65040000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗革命卫队主席誓言在以色列杀害高级顾问后“铲除犹太复国主义政权”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/irgc-chief-vows-to-eradicate-zionist-regime-after-alleged-israeli-killing-of-top-adviser/0000018c-afe2-d45c-a98e-afeee70e0000</link><description>伊朗最高领袖哈梅内伊在叙利亚空袭中丧生的赛义德·拉齐·穆萨维的葬礼上主持祈祷。以色列军队拒绝就穆萨维之死发表评论，但表示已采取一切必要行动来保卫国家</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 11:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/irgc-chief-vows-to-eradicate-zionist-regime-after-alleged-israeli-killing-of-top-adviser/0000018c-afe2-d45c-a98e-afeee70e0000</guid></item><item><title>当 DNA 失败时，这些以色列人类学家正在帮助识别 10 月 7 日死者的身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/when-dna-fails-these-israeli-anthropologists-are-helping-identify-the-october-7-dead/0000018c-afe7-d45c-a98e-afef12ea0000</link><description>Israel Hershkovitz 教授、Hila May 博士和特拉维夫大学的体质人类学专家正在与法医病理学家合作，帮助识别 10 月 7 日的受害者并确定他们的死因，并为未来针对哈马斯恐怖分子建立案件</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/when-dna-fails-these-israeli-anthropologists-are-helping-identify-the-october-7-dead/0000018c-afe7-d45c-a98e-afef12ea0000</guid></item><item><title>这位犹太学者认为散居海外的犹太人必须接受流亡才能拯救犹太教</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-jewish-scholar-believes-diaspora-jews-must-embrace-exile-to-save-judaism/0000018c-af75-d45c-a98e-af7d47ac0000</link><description>绍尔·马吉德曾经倾向于犹太人定居点，但如今他是一位受人尊敬的犹太研究教授，他将自己的世界观定义为“反犹太复国主义”。他的立场设想以色列尊重所有人民的历史并放弃犹太复国主义作为“仅限犹太人”的意识形态</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-jewish-scholar-believes-diaspora-jews-must-embrace-exile-to-save-judaism/0000018c-af75-d45c-a98e-af7d47ac0000</guid></item><item><title>决定泄露后以色列最高法院将加快对司法政变法的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-set-to-expedite-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law-after-decision-leak/0000018c-af76-db94-afbd-af7f3c1b0000</link><description>报告称，八名法官中的大多数支持废除该法律，七名法官反对。司法部长亚里夫·莱文回应称，高等法院不应“在战争期间发布有争议的裁决，即使是在其法官之间”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 09:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-set-to-expedite-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law-after-decision-leak/0000018c-af76-db94-afbd-af7f3c1b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵惊醒后开枪，轻伤战友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-opens-fire-after-waking-up-with-a-start-lightly-wounds-fellow-troops/0000018c-ac24-d22d-a3dd-bd7d13250000</link><description>由于这名士兵的健康状况，尚未就该事件接受军队询问。每天都有数十名士兵被带出加沙接受心理健康官员和精神病医生的检查和治疗</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-opens-fire-after-waking-up-with-a-start-lightly-wounds-fellow-troops/0000018c-ac24-d22d-a3dd-bd7d13250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周三在加沙战斗中丧生的三名以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/idf-names-three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-af30-db94-afbd-af79141f0000</link><description>以色列军方还表示，加沙地带南部和中部还有其他士兵受重伤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/idf-names-three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-af30-db94-afbd-af79141f0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗“独立”代理人的袭击增加了与以色列和美国发生直接冲突的可能性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/attacks-by-irans-independent-proxies-increase-odds-of-direct-clash-with-israel-and-u-s/0000018c-ad16-d22d-a3dd-bd7f52010000</link><description>自以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，德黑兰一直避免与以色列和美国直接对抗。但“抵抗轴心”成员所表现出的独立性使得伊斯兰共和国更难维持合理的推诿，并有可能将其拖入冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/attacks-by-irans-independent-proxies-increase-odds-of-direct-clash-with-israel-and-u-s/0000018c-ad16-d22d-a3dd-bd7f52010000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后，以色列极端正统派部长花了一天时间为地方选举进行政治活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/haredi-israeli-minister-spent-day-after-hamas-massacre-politicking-for-local-election/0000018c-ace9-d22c-a98c-fced9a040000</link><description>当以色列陷入混乱时，梅厄·波鲁什正忙着做交易，以确保他的联合托拉犹太教党和他的儿子埃拉德市长以色列·波鲁什在即将到来的选举中的利益</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/haredi-israeli-minister-spent-day-after-hamas-massacre-politicking-for-local-election/0000018c-ace9-d22c-a98c-fced9a040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队击落从黎巴嫩飞越以色列北部上空的无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-live/suicide-drone-hits-buildings-on-golan-israel-on-very-high-alert-on-lebanon-border/0000018c-ae77-db94-afbd-ae7f8d860000</link><description>以色列外交部长：只要埃尔多安还是土耳其总统，以色列大使就不会回来 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：以色列袭击导致加沙 50 名巴勒斯坦人丧生 ■ 以色列国防军称在加沙城发现了更多隧道 ■ 自杀式无人机损坏戈兰高地的建筑物高地 ■ 以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的名字 ■ 巴勒斯坦人：六人在约旦河西岸无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙至少有 130 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 21,110 人死亡、55,243 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 03:39:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-live/suicide-drone-hits-buildings-on-golan-israel-on-very-high-alert-on-lebanon-border/0000018c-ae77-db94-afbd-ae7f8d860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列副总检察长表示，本-格维尔部非法发放了 14,000 张枪支许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-distributed-14-000-gun-licenses-illegally-israels-deputy-ag-says/0000018c-acea-d45c-a98e-afeef7530000</link><description>本-格维尔的国家安全部利用加沙战争来发挥“创意”，规避有关枪支许可证和所有权的现有法规。司法部认为违法后将其关闭</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-distributed-14-000-gun-licenses-illegally-israels-deputy-ag-says/0000018c-acea-d45c-a98e-afeef7530000</guid></item><item><title>五名以色列士兵因在约旦河西岸袭击巴勒斯坦人而被定居者活动单位解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/five-soldiers-dismissed-from-idf-from-settler-activist-unit-for-assaulting-palestinians/0000018c-ac4b-d22c-a98c-fc6fea220000</link><description>根据巴勒斯坦人的证词，袭击者剥光他们的衣服并殴打他们，在他们身上撒尿，并在他们身上熄灭香烟。以色列国防军最近停止了该部队的行动活动，该部队从西岸前哨基地招募定居青年服兵役</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 21:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/five-soldiers-dismissed-from-idf-from-settler-activist-unit-for-assaulting-palestinians/0000018c-ac4b-d22c-a98c-fc6fea220000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，加沙辛贝特消息来源警告哈马斯将于 10 月初对以色列发动重大袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/shin-bet-source-in-gaza-reportedly-warned-of-major-hamas-attack-in-early-october/0000018c-acab-d22c-a98c-fcefb17e0000</link><description>据12频道报道，消息来源的负责人将这一信息进行了传递，但最终只停留在较低级别，没有到达更高级别的当局。辛贝特对此回应称，“所有现有信息都将受到审查”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:28:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/shin-bet-source-in-gaza-reportedly-warned-of-major-hamas-attack-in-early-october/0000018c-acab-d22c-a98c-fcefb17e0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列高等法院法官准备废除去年夏天通过的关键司法政变法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/report-high-court-justices-poised-to-nullify-key-judicial-coup-law-passed-last-summer/0000018c-ac99-d22d-a3dd-bdf985e20000</link><description>报告称，15 名法官中有 8 名支持废除该法律，该法律取消了法院对政府决定进行司法审查的能力。最终裁决将在未来几周内公布。以色列司法当局拒绝“承认”“未经证实的泄密”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:20:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/report-high-court-justices-poised-to-nullify-key-judicial-coup-law-passed-last-summer/0000018c-ac99-d22d-a3dd-bdf985e20000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨反击本格维尔，但表示他将继续留在以色列紧急政府“以赢得战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/gantz-pushes-back-against-ben-gvir-says-hell-remain-in-emergency-govt-to-win-war/0000018c-ac5c-d22c-a98c-fc7c07010000</link><description>极右翼部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔决定不延长以色列监狱管理局专员的任期，这违反了甘茨政党与利库德集团在 10 月 7 日战争开始后进入紧急政府的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 18:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/gantz-pushes-back-against-ben-gvir-says-hell-remain-in-emergency-govt-to-win-war/0000018c-ac5c-d22c-a98c-fc7c07010000</guid></item></channel></rss>